    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and turn-in precision. It has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry that delivers communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. A mechanically robust example ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
